description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at the Xbox Showcase of 2024 and finally after seeing just games upon games, it's great to see nearly of all of them look quite amazing. Some Franchises that I expected would stay dormant finally showed up such as Gears of War which puts nothing short of a smile on my face. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The 2024 Xbox Showcase Was Actually Amazing...
